505
00:40:25,936 --> 00:40:30,873
只要你们衷心于我 我承诺你们的是整个世界
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}All I ask is your allegiance, and in return, I offer you the world.{\r}

506
00:40:31,241 --> 00:40:33,402
