01:08:41,196 --> 01:08:45,462
- 我只是…你不是… - 我不是什么戴利先生？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- I just... You're not... - I'm not what, Mr. Daley?{\r}

1005
01:08:48,303 --> 01:08:51,295
好吧 你的身体是…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Okay. You're made of...{\r}

1006
01:08:52,641 --> 01:08:54,006
身体是…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Made of...{\r}

1007
01:09:03,585 --> 01:09:07,214
美好的东西 你的身体非常美好 非常了不起
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Wonderful things. You're made of good, wonderful things.{\r}

1008
01:09:13,261 --> 01:09:14,421
走吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Come on.{\r}

1009
01:09:18,900 --> 01:09:21,232
男士们 能帮我们挡一会儿吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Gentlemen, could you buy us some time please?{\r}

1010
01:09:27,576 --> 01:09:28,907
看来只有这个办法了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}It'll have to do.{\r}

1011
01:09:30,445 --> 01:09:33,243
不要！那是人类发明的第一架飞机
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No! That's the first plane ever made!{\r}

1012
01:09:33,348 --> 01:09:36,010
它是用木板做的纸糊的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}It's made out of balsa wood and paper.{\r}

1013
01:09:36,084 --> 01:09:37,847
它是用云杉木和帆布做的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}It's made out of spruce and canvas{\r}

1014
01:09:37,847 --> 01:09:39,611
汇聚了老一代美国人的精巧工艺
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}and good old-fashioned American ingenuity.{\r}

1015
01:09:40,755 --> 01:09:42,222
你到底上不上来？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Are you coming, or what?{\r}

1016
01:09:46,761 --> 01:09:50,197
- 让开！ - 没门
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Out of our way! - I don't think so.{\r}

1017
01:09:51,933 --> 01:09:53,264
他们逃了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}They're getting away!{\r}

1018
01:09:57,405 --> 01:10:00,568
抓稳了戴利先生 这事儿越来越有意思了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hang on, Mr. Daley. Things are about to get interesting.{\r}

1019
01:10:08,049 --> 01:10:10,313
是个女的在开！她是不是疯了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}A lady pilot! Preposterous!{\r}

1020
01:10:10,452 --> 01:10:13,717
- 看清楚 小子们 - 哦 她飞得真好
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Think again, boys! - Oh, she's good.{\r}

1021
01:10:31,473 --> 01:10:33,407
怎么了 怎么了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}What? What?{\r}

1022
01:10:33,475 --> 01:10:35,636
一根线卡住了 我去松开它
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}One of the wires is jammed. I'm going to have to loosen it.{\r}

1023
01:10:35,744 --> 01:10:37,939
- 你来控制方向杆 - 不 我不要！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Here, take the stick! - No! I'm not gonna... No!{\r}

1024
01:10:38,013 --> 01:10:39,571
我知道你还有激情
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I know you've got moxie in you yet.{\r}

1025
01:10:39,648 --> 01:10:43,243
有激情不代表会开飞机 开飞机要飞行执照的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Moxie doesn't fly planes! People who have pilots' licenses fly planes!{\r}

1026
01:10:43,318 --> 01:10:44,842
- 好吧 - 交给你了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Okay. - She's all yours.{\r}

1027
01:10:47,022 --> 01:10:49,252
不要吧！我不要这个
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I don't want it! I don't want the stick!{\r}

1028
01:10:53,128 --> 01:10:55,790
别到处看戴利先生 你在驾驶飞机
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Don't look now, Mr. Daley, but you're flying an airplane!{\r}

1029
01:11:07,342 --> 01:11:09,003
亚伯！开门！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Able! The doors!{\r}

1030
01:11:25,360 --> 01:11:27,954
- 行了！ - 下降！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Got it! - Pull!{\r}

1031
01:11:31,199 --> 01:11:32,564
拉升！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Pull up!{\r}

1032
01:11:38,673 --> 01:11:39,799
好样的！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yes!{\r}

1033
01:11:39,874 --> 01:11:41,569
一路顺风 阿梅莉亚・埃尔哈特
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Godspeed, Amelia Earhart!{\r}

1034
01:11:41,676 --> 01:11:43,075
一路顺风
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Godspeed.{\r}

1035
01:12:21,716 --> 01:12:24,014
你有点紧张啊 蠢猪
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Look a little nervous there, Ramen Noodle.{\r}

1036
01:12:24,085 --> 01:12:26,280
我就当是做热沙按摩
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}'Cause for me, this is like a spa treatment.{\r}

1037
01:12:26,688 --> 01:12:30,886
沙浴能帮助我恢复活力 去角质的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Sand baths are really rejuvenating for the skin. Exfoliates.{\r}

1038
01:12:31,626 --> 01:12:33,025
你放弃了吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Giving up yet?{\r}

1039
01:12:33,194 --> 01:12:35,025
还没有
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Not quite yet, no.{\r}

1040
01:12:35,697 --> 01:12:39,827
我可以让时间流逝的更快些
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}In fact, let's see if we can't make time fly.{\r}

1041
01:12:45,807 --> 01:12:47,468
什么怪声音？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}What is that funny sound?{\r}

1042
01:13:09,230 --> 01:13:10,822
站住！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Stop!{\r}

1043
01:13:12,000 --> 01:13:14,400
站住别动 戴利先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Right there, please, Mr. Daley.{\r}

1044
01:13:14,903 --> 01:13:16,598
哇 哇…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Well. Well, well, well!{\r}

1045
01:13:17,672 --> 01:13:19,162
你的出场很漂亮啊 戴利先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You certainly know how to make an entrance, Mr. Daley.{\r}

1046
01:13:19,274 --> 01:13:20,673
该去挖点援军来了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Time to recruit some backup.{\r}

1047
01:13:20,775 --> 01:13:23,243
你朋友快淹死了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I hope for your little friend's sake, here,{\r}

1048
01:13:23,311 --> 01:13:25,677
但愿你已经想到了密码
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}that you also figured out the combination.{\r}

1049
01:13:25,780 --> 01:13:27,304
- 把杰德给我 - 哦 不不不
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Give me Jed. - Oh, no, no, no.{\r}

1050
01:13:27,415 --> 01:13:30,145
先给我密码 还有金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}First, give me the combination and hand over that tablet.{\r}

1051
01:13:30,251 --> 01:13:31,843
我会把金牌和密码给你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I'll give you the tablet and the combination{\r}

1052
01:13:31,953 --> 01:13:33,614
不过你先放了我的朋友们 还有把他给我
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}when you release my friends and give him back to me.{\r}

1053
01:13:33,755 --> 01:13:37,589
我愿意什么时候放人就什么时候放人
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I shall release what I want to release the moment I want to release it.{\r}

1054
01:13:37,659 --> 01:13:39,286
好极了 那我什么时候愿意给你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Great. And I'll release what I want to release{\r}

1055
01:13:39,360 --> 01:13:41,089
我就什么时候给你 怎么样？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}at the exact moment that I want to release it, okay?{\r}

1056
01:13:41,162 --> 01:13:43,858
给我密码和金牌 马上
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Tell me the combination and give me that tablet right now{\r}

1057
01:13:43,965 --> 01:13:45,933
否则我就杀光你的朋友
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}or I shall kill all of your friends,{\r}

1058
01:13:46,000 --> 01:13:48,798
首先拿这个胡子拉楂的小牛仔开刀
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}starting with the little shaggy-headed little cowman here.{\r}

1059
01:13:48,870 --> 01:13:52,271
我才不胡子拉楂 铁人 把这个坏蛋交给我
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I ain't shaggy-headed! Gigantor, let me take this guy!{\r}

1060
01:13:52,340 --> 01:13:54,968
别担心 我能处理 你不先放了我的朋友
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Don't worry, I got this handled. You don't want to give me my friends,{\r}

1061
01:13:55,043 --> 01:13:56,943
你就别想拿到密码和金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}then you're not gonna get your combination or your tablet.{\r}

1062
01:13:57,011 --> 01:13:58,444
- 好吧 你给我听好 - 好的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- All right, I'll tell you what. - Good.{\r}

1063
01:13:58,513 --> 01:14:01,380
我的外号不是什么值得信赖的卡门拉
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}They didn't call me Kahmunrah the Trustworthy for nothing.{\r}

1064
01:14:01,483 --> 01:14:04,145
给你 我的外号不叫值得信赖的卡门拉
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Here you go. They didn't call me Kahmunrah the Trustworthy!{\r}

1065
01:14:04,219 --> 01:14:06,153
他们叫我嗜血卡门拉
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}They called me Kahmunrah the Bloodthirsty,{\r}

1066
01:14:06,221 --> 01:14:09,850
这个卡门拉想要什么
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}who kills whoever doesn't give Kahmunrah exactly what he wants{\r}

1067
01:14:09,958 --> 01:14:12,256
就要立刻得到
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}in the moment that he wants it, which is right now,{\r}

1068
01:14:12,327 --> 01:14:15,524
这个卡门拉现在要的就是金牌和密码
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}when I had also better get the combination and the tablet!{\r}

1069
01:14:16,598 --> 01:14:19,123
- 你的外号很长啊 - 用埃及语会短一些
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- That's what they called you? - It was shorter in Egyptian.{\r}

1070
01:14:19,200 --> 01:14:20,929
很好 把他给我 我就给你密码和金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Great, I'll give you the combination after you give him back.{\r}

1071
01:14:21,002 --> 01:14:24,062
我看你再敢碰它一下 我就立刻杀了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}How dare you? If you touch that again, I shall kill you right now.{\r}

1072
01:14:24,139 --> 01:14:25,766
- 好吧 - 别碰它
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Okay. - Do not touch this.{\r}

1073
01:14:25,840 --> 01:14:28,707
- 这里是禁止触碰区域！ - 好 好吧…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- This is a no-touching zone! - Good. Well, then...{\r}

1074
01:14:28,777 --> 01:14:32,804
哦上帝 我简直不敢相信你又过界了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, my God! I can't believe you reached across like that again!{\r}

1075
01:14:32,881 --> 01:14:36,317
难以置信 上帝 我真想马上杀了你…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I can't even believe it! Oh, God, I want to kill you right...{\r}

1076
01:14:36,384 --> 01:14:40,115
要不是你知道密码 你早就没命了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}If you didn't know this combination, you'd be so dead right now,{\r}

1077
01:14:40,188 --> 01:14:43,180
- 你会死的很难看 - 可惜我知道密码
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- it would be unbelievable. - Great, but I do know the combination.{\r}

1078
01:14:43,391 --> 01:14:47,350
不许你的手越过这条线
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Don't cross this line with your hand!{\r}

1079
01:14:47,462 --> 01:14:53,367
胆大包天！如果你再嗦一句 我就杀了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}How dare you! If you speak again, I'm going to kill you.{\r}

1080
01:14:53,468 --> 01:14:54,958
听明白没有？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Do you understand this?{\r}

1081
01:14:55,036 --> 01:14:56,901
不许说话 上帝 我看到你嘴巴动了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Don't say it! Oh, God, I see you getting ready.{\r}

1082
01:14:57,005 --> 01:14:59,132
- 我没想开口说话 - 哦 上帝 不许说话
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- I wasn't gonna say anything. - Oh, my God, don't say anything.{\r}

1083
01:14:59,207 --> 01:15:01,334
你再说一句我就掐死你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I shall murder you if you talk again.{\r}

1084
01:15:01,409 --> 01:15:06,540
把金牌和密码给我
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Now give me that tablet and tell me the combination.{\r}

1085
01:15:06,815 --> 01:15:09,477
可以 你先放了杰德还有我的朋友
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Okay. After you give me Jed and release my friends.{\r}

1086
01:15:10,351 --> 01:15:11,750
- 你又犯规了 - 什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- You did all three! - What?{\r}

1087
01:15:11,853 --> 01:15:13,753
你不仅说话了而且又把手伸过来了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You spoke and you reached your hand across!{\r}

1088
01:15:13,855 --> 01:15:15,720
听着 我可以跟你绕一晚上
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Look. I can talk to you about this all night, okay?{\r}

1089
01:15:15,824 --> 01:15:17,189
- 不如这样 - 你给我听好…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- How about this? - Look, just give...{\r}

1090
01:15:17,258 --> 01:15:19,556
我可以先不杀你 虽然我很想很想杀了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}How about I don't kill you right now, like I really, really want to,{\r}

1091
01:15:19,661 --> 01:15:21,686
我给你五秒钟的时间
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}and I give you precisely five seconds{\r}

1092
01:15:21,763 --> 01:15:24,493
交出金牌和密码
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}to give me that tablet and tell me the combination?{\r}

1093
01:15:24,566 --> 01:15:28,161
我们知道密码了 是圆周率
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}We already got the combination. It's pi.{\r}

1094
01:15:28,570 --> 01:15:33,269
- 3.14159265 - 不！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- 3.14159265. - No!{\r}

1095
01:15:33,374 --> 01:15:35,001
- 嘿 - 对不起
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Hey. - Sorry.{\r}

1096
01:15:35,743 --> 01:15:41,773
这个怪老头 还会唱歌 唱起来像只金丝雀
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}So Crazy Hair here, he sang. Oh, did he sing! Like a canary.{\r}

1097
01:15:42,517 --> 01:15:43,950
对不起 拉瑞
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I'm sorry, Larry.{\r}

1098
01:15:44,052 --> 01:15:46,543
你少废话！忘了教训了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Enough out of you! Remember what happened last time?{\r}

1099
01:15:46,921 --> 01:15:48,445
- 住手 - 蠢货
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- That's enough. - Stupid man.{\r}

1100
01:15:51,559 --> 01:15:53,959
- 你没事吧？ - 没事 谢谢
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- You okay? - Yeah, thanks.{\r}

1101
01:15:54,062 --> 01:15:56,530
你肯定气坏了吧 拉瑞
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Must be a real bummer for you, Larry,{\r}

1102
01:15:57,465 --> 01:16:01,526
你失去了所有的筹码
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}knowing that all of your valiant efforts were, in the end, for naught.{\r}

1103
01:16:02,904 --> 01:16:06,601
你肯定沮丧到不行
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}What a terrible disappointment you must be to yourself.{\r}

1104
01:16:16,284 --> 01:16:18,309
听到嗡嗡声了没有？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Do you hear that humming sound?{\r}

1105
01:16:19,921 --> 01:16:21,946
知道这是什么声音吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Do you know what that sound is?{\r}

1106
01:16:24,058 --> 01:16:25,491
我在用修辞
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}It's rhetorical.{\r}

1107
01:16:26,160 --> 01:16:29,789
那就是末日的声音
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}That is the sound of the End.{\r}

1108
01:16:37,639 --> 01:16:39,163
对不起 杰德
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I'm sorry, Jed.{\r}

1109
01:16:40,275 --> 01:16:41,936
你尽力了铁人
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You did your best, Gigantor.{\r}

1110
01:16:42,577 --> 01:16:44,841
见鬼 我们差点就赢了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Dadgum it, we almost had him, too.{\r}

1111
01:16:44,946 --> 01:16:48,143
不 我是说我很抱歉 前几年我一直不在博物馆
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No, I mean, I'm sorry I wasn't around the last couple of years at the museum.{\r}

1112
01:16:48,750 --> 01:16:52,686
- 否则这一切都不会发生 - 你还不明白吗 铁人？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Maybe none of this would have happened. - You don't get it, do you, Gigantor?{\r}

1113
01:16:52,787 --> 01:16:55,187
我打给你不是我们需要帮助
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I didn't call you 'cause we needed your help.{\r}

1114
01:16:55,290 --> 01:16:56,951
我们确实有点小麻烦
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Sure, we were in a little pickle,{\r}

1115
01:16:57,025 --> 01:16:58,515
但这不是我第一次
