1129
01:18:07,762 --> 01:18:11,163
我的军队 前进！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Horus, Ra, my warriors, come forth!{\r}

1130
01:18:11,666 --> 01:18:16,603
把拉瑞・戴利和他的朋友送进地狱！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Send Larry Daley and his friends to their doom!{\r}

1131
01:18:41,429 --> 01:18:43,056
住手！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Halt!{\r}

1132
01:18:44,065 --> 01:18:46,932
伟大的奥克塔维厄斯回来了！
