1134
01:18:53,441 --> 01:18:56,740
一只松鼠！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}the squirrel!{\r}

1135
01:18:59,380 --> 01:19:02,406
前进 我的战马！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Forward now, my mighty steed!{\r}

1136
01:19:05,720 --> 01:19:08,621
悠着点 姑娘
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Whoa, girl! Easy.{\r}

1137
01:19:08,723 --> 01:19:10,884
你选择缴械投降
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Do you wish to surrender honorably?{\r}

1138
01:19:10,958 --> 01:19:14,223
还是血溅沙场？
