{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- No. - No? Not good. Not good at all.{\r}

1172
01:22:06,434 --> 01:22:08,868
- 感觉不好 - 当然 我也就能动动嘴皮子
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- That's not good. - Sure, I talk a good game,{\r}

1173
01:22:08,936 --> 01:22:11,700
干真的不行 我不配肩膀上的军衔
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}but the truth of the matter is, I don't deserve these stars.{\r}

1174
01:22:13,207 --> 01:22:16,540
人们永远只记得我的失败
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I will always be famous for my biggest failure.{\r}

1175
01:22:19,647 --> 01:22:20,739
嘿
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey.{\r}

1176
01:22:21,115 --> 01:22:23,106
过去的就让它过去 好吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}The past is the past, okay?{\r}

1177
01:22:23,818 --> 01:22:26,548
现在 当下 就在今夜
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Right now, this moment, this night,{\r}

1178
01:22:28,022 --> 01:22:29,922
这场战役将永垂青史
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}this is what you're gonna be remembered for.{\r}

1179
01:22:31,659 --> 01:22:33,320
这是你的最后一战
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}This is your last stand.{\r}

1180
01:22:51,012 --> 01:22:53,503
- 我们需要一位领袖 - 是啊 他们需要领袖
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- They need a leader. - Yeah, they need a leader.{\r}

1181
01:22:55,449 --> 01:22:57,679
是吗？你愿意去领导他们吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah? You want to be their leader, huh?{\r}

1182
01:22:58,753 --> 01:23:00,516
- 是 我愿意 - 那就站起来！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Yeah, I do. - Let's do this!{\r}

1183
01:23:01,155 --> 01:23:02,281
- 怎么样？ - 好
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- All right? - Yeah.{\r}

1184
01:23:02,356 --> 01:23:03,721
我们走！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Let's go!{\r}

1185
01:23:06,027 --> 01:23:07,426
太糟了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Not good!{\r}

1186
01:23:07,928 --> 01:23:08,917
拉瑞！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Larry!{\r}

1187
01:23:09,664 --> 01:23:10,756
嘿 亚伯！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, Able!{\r}

1188
01:23:10,831 --> 01:23:11,820
我需要帮助
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I want to help!{\r}

1189
01:23:11,966 --> 01:23:13,058
哦 好的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, great.{\r}

1190
01:23:13,134 --> 01:23:14,829
你是谁？这是我的博物馆
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Who are you? This is my museum!{\r}

1191
01:23:15,202 --> 01:23:16,965
他是我的人 你走开
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Well, he's my human. Back off!{\r}

1192
01:23:17,171 --> 01:23:18,729
你尽管拉人 你这个野蛮人
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You need all the help you can get, Jungle-Dweller!{\r}

1193
01:23:19,340 --> 01:23:20,329
少废话 你这个太空佬
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Get over yourself space snob!{\r}

1194
01:23:20,408 --> 01:23:21,432
伙计们！嘿 伙计们！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Guys! Hey, guys!{\r}

1195
01:23:21,509 --> 01:23:23,374
现在不是争这些的时候 好吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}This is not the time to get into this, all right?{\r}

1196
01:23:25,646 --> 01:23:26,977
德克斯特 你知道规矩
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Dexter, you know better.{\r}

1197
01:23:28,949 --> 01:23:30,814
好吗 再胡闹就请你们吃耳光
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}All right? That's what happens when you do that!{\r}

1198
01:23:30,885 --> 01:23:32,216
给你一耳光
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You get that.{\r}

1199
01:23:39,460 --> 01:23:41,792
住手 都给我住手！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Stop! Just stop! Stop!{\r}

1200
01:23:42,363 --> 01:23:45,355
听着 你们都是高贵的僧帽猴
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Now, listen. You're both proud capuchin!{\r}

1201
01:23:46,233 --> 01:23:48,030
应该一直对外 抗击外敌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You need to concentrate on slapping the enemy!{\r}

1202
01:23:51,906 --> 01:23:53,203
团结起来 行吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Keep it together, all right?{\r}

1203
01:23:53,307 --> 01:23:55,207
快 冲上去 给我打
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Come on, let's go! Let's do it!{\r}

1204
01:23:57,178 --> 01:24:00,011
- 杰迪戴亚 大家需要我们 - 我恐怕不行了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Jedediah! They need us! - I ain't gonna make it!{\r}

1205
01:24:00,414 --> 01:24:02,882
恐怕我的日子到头了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Afraid this cowboy's been to his last hoedown.{\r}

1206
01:24:03,384 --> 01:24:09,220
奥克塔维厄斯 记住我的精神 自由 狂野…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Octavius, remember me as I was, wild, and free, and...{\r}

1207
01:24:10,491 --> 01:24:13,927
- 还不是说遗言的时候 - 我还没说完
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- No need for final words. - I'm not finished yet.{\r}

1208
01:24:14,362 --> 01:24:16,125
我还想回忆一下我们的那段事
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I want to get to the story of our relationship,{\r}

1209
01:24:16,197 --> 01:24:18,495
我们是怎么从敌人变成朋友的
