1210
01:24:18,666 --> 01:24:20,998
- 不要！ - 你想哭就哭吧！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- No! - It'll make you cry!{\r}

1211
01:24:21,068 --> 01:24:24,333
不！因为你还死不了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No! Because you are going to live!{\r}

1212
01:24:35,316 --> 01:24:37,784
- 该我们上场了 - 拿着剑
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Let's go to work. - Have a sword.{\r}

1213
01:24:38,919 --> 01:24:40,352
拿剑来！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Sword!{\r}

1214
01:24:57,571 --> 01:24:59,232
上面！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Incoming!{\r}

1215
01:25:18,492 --> 01:25:19,720
好疼
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}That smarts.{\r}

1216
01:25:23,330 --> 01:25:26,060
你打 你踢！ 你打 你踢！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You smack, you kick! You smack, you kick!{\r}

1217
01:25:26,133 --> 01:25:29,466
你打 你踢！ 干得漂亮 伙计们！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You smack, you kick! Teamwork, fellas! Wunderbar!{\r}

1218
01:25:33,407 --> 01:25:34,772
你们好啊 伙计们！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}How you doing, fellas?{\r}

1219
01:26:05,940 --> 01:26:07,669
- 你还好吗？ - 再好没有
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Are you all right? - Never better.{\r}

1220
01:26:07,775 --> 01:26:09,936
听着 一看到我的信号就立刻打开门
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Listen, when I give you the signal, I want you to open the gate.{\r}

1221
01:26:10,010 --> 01:26:12,843
- 看来你成竹在胸 - 我要去搞点小破坏
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- I take it you have a plan. - I'm gonna divide the house.{\r}

1222
01:26:17,985 --> 01:26:20,453
金牌给我 马上！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}The tablet! Now!{\r}

1223
01:26:20,521 --> 01:26:21,954
好的 当然 我会给你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Okay, sure, you can have it.{\r}

1224
01:26:22,022 --> 01:26:24,013
告诉我你们谁是头 我就给他
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Just tell me who the boss is and I'll give it to you.{\r}

1225
01:26:24,124 --> 01:26:26,615
要不我给卡门拉? 他看上去是你们头 不是吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Or should I give it to Kahmunrah? He's your master, right?{\r}

1226
01:26:26,894 --> 01:26:28,725
放屁 他才不是什么头
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Nyet! He is not our master!{\r}

1227
01:26:28,725 --> 01:26:30,557
是吗？我看一直是他在说了算
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Really? 'Cause he acts like he is.{\r}

1228
01:26:30,664 --> 01:26:32,655
算了 你就告诉我你们谁是头 我就给谁
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}But fine, just tell me who the boss is and you can have it.{\r}

1229
01:26:32,733 --> 01:26:35,133
我是头！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey! That'd be me.{\r}

1230
01:26:36,504 --> 01:26:39,667
他是个农民 我才是这里唯一有贵族血统的人
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}This man is a peasant! I am the only one here of noble birth!{\r}

1231
01:26:39,740 --> 01:26:42,709
是吗？可是他看上去有更多勋章 帽子也更大 不过…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Really? 'Cause he's got more medals and a bigger hat, but...{\r}

1232
01:26:42,810 --> 01:26:44,835
- 谢谢 - 你确实有很多勋章
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Thank you. - You might got a lot of medals,{\r}

1233
01:26:44,912 --> 01:26:47,540
但是你要再敢用你的小手碰一下金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}but you put one of your little child hands on that tablet again,{\r}

1234
01:26:47,648 --> 01:26:50,481
我就要你好看
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}it'll be the last thing them tiny little mitts of yours ever touch.{\r}

1235
01:26:50,551 --> 01:26:52,416
你干嘛要伤害小拿拿？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Why would you touch little Nippy?{\r}

1236
01:26:54,488 --> 01:26:55,853
我能自己解决 好吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I can handle this, okay?{\r}

1237
01:26:55,923 --> 01:26:59,017
你什么也解决不了 你连话都说不清楚 蠢货！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You can handle nothing! You can barely speak, you fool!{\r}

1238
01:26:59,093 --> 01:27:03,029
没问题 你要是吗 我给你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You know what? No problem. I'll give it to you. You see that?{\r}

1239
01:27:06,901 --> 01:27:08,493
你这个小杂种
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, you're a spunky little fella!{\r}

1240
01:27:12,706 --> 01:27:18,110
干得漂亮 戴利先生 让他们自相残杀
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Very clever, Mr. Daley, getting them to fight amongst themselves.{\r}

1241
01:27:18,212 --> 01:27:22,012
对 我不敢邀功 这主意是亚伯拉罕・林肯想出来的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah. I can't really take credit. It was Abraham Lincoln's idea.{\r}

1242
01:27:22,082 --> 01:27:24,448
家庭不睦 万事不兴…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You know, a house divided can't...{\r}

1243
01:27:25,286 --> 01:27:27,277
- 还做得不够 - 没错
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Doesn't do well. - Yes, well,{\r}

1244
01:27:27,388 --> 01:27:31,085
刚才你就应该自己逃命的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}you should have saved yourself when you had the chance,{\r}

1245
01:27:32,693 --> 01:27:34,957
可惜你又落在了我手里
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}because now I shall have the tremendous pleasure{\r}

1246
01:27:35,362 --> 01:27:36,693
我现在最想做的事就是亲手杀了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}of killing you myself!{\r}

1247
01:28:27,481 --> 01:28:28,846
你到底是什么人？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}What are you?{\r}

1248
01:28:31,018 --> 01:28:32,451
我是个守卫
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I'm the night guard.{\r}

1249
01:28:33,120 --> 01:28:35,918
不！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No!{\r}

1250
01:28:45,099 --> 01:28:47,033
胜利属于我们！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Victory is ours!{\r}

1251
01:28:48,802 --> 01:28:49,962
耶！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah!{\r}

1252
01:28:55,943 --> 01:28:57,638
我说什么来着！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}That's what I'm talking about!{\r}

1253
01:28:57,711 --> 01:28:59,576
耶！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah!{\r}

1254
01:29:04,451 --> 01:29:06,885
我看到有个人终于找回他的激情了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I'd say somebody found his moxie.{\r}

1255
01:29:08,989 --> 01:29:10,820
史密森尼战役
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}The Battle of the Smithsonian.{\r}

1256
01:29:12,459 --> 01:29:15,860
将是一场永远不为人知的伟大战役
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Perhaps the greatest battle the world will never know.{\r}

1257
01:29:18,232 --> 01:29:19,563
我们都见证了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}We'll know.{\r}

1258
01:29:22,970 --> 01:29:24,562
是啊
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah.{\r}

1259
01:29:26,373 --> 01:29:29,171
噢 老天 还有一个小时就天亮了 我得把你们都弄回去
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, man, I got an hour till sunrise. I got to get you guys back.{\r}

1260
01:29:29,243 --> 01:29:33,236
我不得不提醒你铁人 那儿的人不再需要我们了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}In case you forgot, Gigantor, they don't want us there anymore.{\r}

1261
01:29:33,347 --> 01:29:34,712
不 我需要
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Well, I do.{\r}

1262
01:29:38,385 --> 01:29:41,081
嘿 可以载我们一程吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, think you could hook us up with a ride?{\r}

1263
01:29:42,389 --> 01:29:44,220
当然 我很荣幸
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}My pleasure, of course.{\r}

1264
01:29:45,025 --> 01:29:48,517
稍等 我还有件事要办
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hang on a second. One last thing I got to take care of.{\r}

1265
01:29:49,530 --> 01:29:52,431
快 孩子！来啊
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Come on, boy! Come on, come on!{\r}

1266
01:29:53,167 --> 01:29:54,361
跳进去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Get in there!{\r}

1267
01:29:57,237 --> 01:29:58,670
很舒服吧？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Feels good, right?{\r}

1268
01:30:01,775 --> 01:30:05,677
别客气！ 记得天亮前一定要回去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You're welcome! Just get back inside by sunrise, okay?{\r}

1269
01:30:19,426 --> 01:30:22,327
这真是一个光明的时代
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}These are promising days, indeed.{\r}

1270
01:30:45,486 --> 01:30:47,147
好了 伙计们 动作快
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}All right. Hey, come on, guys.{\r}

1271
01:30:47,254 --> 01:30:50,314
记得和同伴呆在一起
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Remember, stay with your buddy, all right?{\r}

1272
01:30:50,424 --> 01:30:51,789
好 好
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Good, good.{\r}

1273
01:31:02,770 --> 01:31:04,499
好了 你回到该回的地方了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Well, you're back where you belong.{\r}

1274
01:31:06,640 --> 01:31:08,437
我想是的
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah. Think so.{\r}

1275
01:31:15,249 --> 01:31:16,739
我想我该走了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I guess I should be going.{\r}

1276
01:31:19,153 --> 01:31:20,677
阿梅莉亚
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, Amelia.{\r}

1277
01:31:23,190 --> 01:31:25,920
早些时候我想告诉你的那件事…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}That thing that I was trying to tell you about earlier...{\r}

1278
01:31:28,762 --> 01:31:31,253
我真的很难说出口
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}There's not really an easy way to put this,{\r}

1279
01:31:32,332 --> 01:31:36,359
- 但是 一旦天亮… - 我知道会发生什么 戴利先生
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- but, in the morning... - I know what's coming, Mr. Daley.{\r}

1280
01:31:36,470 --> 01:31:37,835
我一直知道
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I've always known.{\r}

1281
01:31:39,606 --> 01:31:41,301
不过没关系
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}But it doesn't matter.{\r}

1282
01:31:41,375 --> 01:31:45,334
在一夜之间 你给了我一生都未曾体验过的冒险经历
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}You've given me the adventure of a lifetime in one night.{\r}

1283
01:31:47,481 --> 01:31:50,882
我觉得今天的日出一定特别美丽
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}And I have a feeling it's going to be a beautiful sunrise.{\r}

1284
01:31:59,226 --> 01:32:00,716
要快乐
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Have fun.{\r}

1285
01:32:10,003 --> 01:32:11,334
谢谢
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Thanks.{\r}

1286
01:33:02,556 --> 01:33:06,356
不知道你怎么想 伙计 可这个老牛仔才攻到二垒
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I don't know about you fellas, but this old cowboy just got to second base.{\r}

1287
01:33:09,263 --> 01:33:11,663
- 她飞走了 - 头也不回…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- There she goes. - Straight towards...{\r}

1288
01:33:13,233 --> 01:33:14,928
加拿大
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Canada.{\r}

1289
01:33:15,936 --> 01:33:17,767
她在往加拿大飞
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}She's heading to Canada.{\r}

1290
01:33:20,107 --> 01:33:22,075
航向正确
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No, now she course-corrected.{\r}

1291
01:33:26,680 --> 01:33:28,011
去地下室 伙计们
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Here, head on downstairs, guys.{\r}

1292
01:33:28,081 --> 01:33:29,548
- 好的 - 晚上好 拉瑞
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- All righty. - Good night, Larry.{\r}

1293
01:33:29,616 --> 01:33:31,083
孩子 你好吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, boy, how's it going?{\r}

1294
01:33:32,686 --> 01:33:35,450
劳伦斯！谢谢你把他们都带回来
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Lawrence! Bless you for bringing them back.{\r}

1295
01:33:35,555 --> 01:33:38,251
你干的真是太漂亮了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}And might I say, a hearty well-done is in order.{\r}

1296
01:33:38,358 --> 01:33:41,794
可是他们不能在地下室躲一辈子
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}And may I also point out, they cannot hide in the basement forever.{\r}

1297
01:33:41,862 --> 01:33:43,489
不 我已经想到办法了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah. No, I think I got that figured out.{\r}

1298
01:33:43,563 --> 01:33:44,689
- 真的 - 对
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Really? - Yeah.{\r}

1299
01:33:44,765 --> 01:33:46,562
日出 笨瓜
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Sun come, dum-dum.{\r}

1300
01:33:47,567 --> 01:33:49,762
我们摩艾朋友说的对 日出即将来临
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Our moai friend is right. The dawn will soon be upon us.{\r}

1301
01:33:49,870 --> 01:33:51,303
泰德
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, Teddy.{\r}

1302
01:33:51,371 --> 01:33:52,861
还记得那天晚上你和我说的吗
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Remember the other night you were saying something{\r}

1303
01:33:52,940 --> 01:33:54,237
你说幸福的关键是
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}about the key to happiness?{\r}

1304
01:33:54,308 --> 01:33:56,037
- 我说了吗？ - 你说：“幸福的关键是…”
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Did I? - You said, "The key to happiness is..."{\r}

1305
01:33:56,109 --> 01:33:58,577
然后太阳出来你就冻住了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}And then the sun came up and you froze.{\r}

1306
01:33:58,645 --> 01:34:00,408
- 我想我知道答案了 - 是吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- I think I got it figured out. - Yes?{\r}

1307
01:34:00,914 --> 01:34:04,213
就是做你爱做的事 对不对 和你爱的人在一起
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}It's doing what you love, isn't it? With people you love.{\r}

1308
01:34:06,486 --> 01:34:08,317
其实 我想说的是“锻炼身体”
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Actually, I was going to say "physical exercise",{\r}

1309
01:34:08,422 --> 01:34:09,821
不过你说的也不错
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}but the love thing's good, too.{\r}

1310
01:34:15,562 --> 01:34:17,757
- 劳伦斯 - 什么
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Lawrence! - Yeah.{\r}

1311
01:34:20,100 --> 01:34:21,761
欢迎回家 孩子
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Welcome home, son.{\r}

1312
01:34:24,137 --> 01:34:25,570
谢谢
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Thanks.{\r}

1313
01:34:40,487 --> 01:34:44,116
朋友们 漫长的等待终于结束 经过了2个月的整修
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Well, folks, the wait is over. After two months of renovation,{\r}

1314
01:34:44,191 --> 01:34:47,922
今夜 自然历史博物馆将重新对公众开放
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}tonight, The Museum of Natural History reopens its doors to the public.{\r}

1315
01:34:47,995 --> 01:34:50,361
如你所见 纽约市民正迫不及待的涌进博物馆
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}As you can see, New Yorkers are flooding in,{\r}

1316
01:34:50,464 --> 01:34:52,989
想亲身体验博物馆
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}eager to see just what changes are in store.{\r}

1317
01:34:53,100 --> 01:34:54,829
新推出的夜游项目
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}With its new, extended night hours,{\r}

1318
01:34:54,935 --> 01:34:57,631
据说夜间博物馆的展品 比以往更加栩栩如生
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}we're told the museum will be more lively than ever.{\r}

1319
01:35:11,718 --> 01:35:14,346
都过了这么久了 这身制服倒还合身
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I see the uniform still fits after these long, long years.{\r}

1320
01:35:14,454 --> 01:35:16,820
是啊 不过也没过多久嘛…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah, yeah. Really hasn't been that long, but...{\r}

1321
01:35:17,724 --> 01:35:21,683
那么 这场喜庆回归的代价是什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}So, to what do we owe this "triumphant" return?{\r}

1322
01:35:21,795 --> 01:35:25,231
还是适应不了商场 被裁了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Not cut out for the "corporate" jungle after all. Got fired.{\r}

1323
01:35:27,034 --> 01:35:30,003
实际上 我把公司卖了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No, actually, I sold my company.{\r}

1324
01:35:30,070 --> 01:35:33,039
这个世界的变化令人难以捉摸
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}The world doth move in mysterious ways.{\r}

1325
01:35:33,140 --> 01:35:35,973
前一天我们还在清理所有老展品
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}One day, we've got to get rid of everything old,{\r}

1326
01:35:36,043 --> 01:35:42,073
后一天 一个富有的无名氏突然捐助了博物馆一大笔资金
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}the next, a rich, anonymous donor gives a huge endowment.{\r}

1327
01:35:42,182 --> 01:35:46,141
条件就是 保持所有老展品不变…
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}With a proviso: Everything stays the same. So...{\r}

1328
01:35:50,824 --> 01:35:53,190
- 很明显 也不是一点没变 - 不是
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Well, not exactly the same, obviously. - No.{\r}

1329
01:35:53,260 --> 01:35:56,195
注意 女士们先生们 我是西奥多・罗斯福
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Bully, lads and ladies, the name is Theodore Roosevelt,{\r}

1330
01:35:56,263 --> 01:36:01,098
一个自然主义者 又名狂野骑士 美国的第26任总统
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}naturalist, Rough Rider and twenty-sixth President of these great United States.{\r}

1331
01:36:01,201 --> 01:36:04,693
跟上 孩子 冒险开始 劳伦斯
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Come along, lad. The hunt is afoot. Lawrence.{\r}

1332
01:36:10,243 --> 01:36:13,110
嘿 你们这些笨瓜给我带口香糖吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Hey, you dum-dums bring me gum-gum?{\r}

1333
01:36:20,954 --> 01:36:24,287
大约3000年前 我父母给了我这块金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}My parents gave me this tablet some 3,000 years ago,{\r}

1334
01:36:24,391 --> 01:36:28,555
这是埃及人民最至高无上的宝物
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}entrusting me with one of my people's most prized possessions.{\r}

1335
01:36:28,628 --> 01:36:31,461
- 它有什么用？ - 什么用？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Does it do anything? - Do anything?{\r}

1336
01:36:31,565 --> 01:36:33,590
对 如果没用的话要它来干嘛？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Yeah. What's the point if it doesn't do anything?{\r}

1337
01:36:34,734 --> 01:36:35,826
告诉他们
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Tell 'em{\r}

1338
01:36:35,902 --> 01:36:38,166
实际上 它是一块复活金牌
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Actually, it has a magical power{\r}

1339
01:36:38,166 --> 01:36:40,430
可以让这里的展览品都活过来
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}that brings all the exhibits to life.{\r}

1340
01:36:40,540 --> 01:36:41,973
好了 别开玩笑 它到底有什么用？
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}No, really, what's it do?{\r}

1341
01:36:43,643 --> 01:36:46,134
没用 只是装饰品
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Nothing. It's just for decoration.{\r}

1342
01:36:46,246 --> 01:36:47,577
我就知道
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}I knew it.{\r}

1343
01:36:48,748 --> 01:36:52,616
这里烂透了 这个恐龙看上去一点都不真实
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}This place is lame. This thing doesn't even look real.{\r}

1344
01:36:52,719 --> 01:36:55,813
没错 老兄 这里的电动技术太落后了
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}Seriously, dude, these animatronics suck.{\r}

1345
01:37:05,298 --> 01:37:06,731
- 猛犸象？ - 是啊
{\fscx75\fscy75\3c&HFF0000&}- Mammoth? - Yeah.{\r}

1346
01:37:06,800 --> 01:37:08,233
绝种了！
